{"tid":272882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 驚嚇！羊唔食草走去食雞仔？仲要細心咀嚼完至吞！","createTime":"2017-06-06T06:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T06:49:56.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03b05139f73a6fd0117a37dc9fe2b9375c7208f6","tid":272882,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"相信在大家的印象中羊都是以吃草為主，但如果突然「開葷」肯定會嚇壞不少人！日前中國有一名女子在路邊驚見羊張口「活吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」小雞的畫面，看得讓她崩潰直喊：「媽呀還在嚼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」。<br />\n<br />\n一名網友在《臉書》社團「爆笑公社」上傳一段影片，並表示「這羊太危險&hellip;」，影片中可以看到路邊站著一隻羊，但嘴巴卻不停地在咀嚼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而羊的面前更放有4籃「活生生」的小雞，但近看卻發現這隻羊正在享用牠的小雞大餐，且吃完一隻又咬起另外一隻，嚇到讓掌鏡的女子直喊：「媽呀！羊把雞給吃了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">全文（有片）：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170604/1132874/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170604%2F1132874%2F&d=4SpXZaLj5ob%2B9IFCabkP20%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5d6ba667\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170604/1132874/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n許多網友看到影片後直說「哇靠！牠真的把小雞給吃了！」、「這是披著羊皮的狼嗎？」、「原來羊也會開葷」、「第一次知道羊也會吃肉。」、「抱歉我之前真的都當你是吃素的.....」。更有人猜測這隻羊可能太餓了，因此才會出現這種情況。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"48ea923cae43eb5237cc1b022bcac92022b83a39","tid":272882,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:49:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170604/640_74b1f1cbd2865a399646e3beac1cf4a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170604%2F640_74b1f1cbd2865a399646e3beac1cf4a7.jpg&h=3bd49e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170604/640_f2e11aa9c3e1c77f8f2cfcc6afdfb514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170604%2F640_f2e11aa9c3e1c77f8f2cfcc6afdfb514.jpg&h=33feda33&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}